This paper deals with a logical framework for reasoning about knowledge and updates, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of logic in computer science (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper introduces a new dynamic operator for updating knowledge about constants, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses multi-agent scenarios, which is a topic in multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and game theory (cs.GT).
